<td data-valign="top"><p><span id="img_06800"></span> <img src="img/06800.jpg" alt="T" /></p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>THIGEAM an diugh ’an t-Athair,<br />
Thigeam an diugh ’an Mhac,<br />
Thigeam ’an Spiorad neartor naomh;<br />
Thigeam an diugh le Dia,<br />
Thigeam an diugh le Criosd,<br />
Thigeam le Spiorad iocshlaint chaomh.</p>
<p>Dia, agus Spiorad, agus Ios,<br />
Bho mhullach mo chinn,<br />
Gu iochdar mo bhonn;<br />
Thigeam le mo chliu,<br />
Falbham le mo theasd,<br />
Thigeam thugad, Iosa--<br />
     Iosa, dean mo leasd.</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>COME I this day to the Father,<br />
Come I this day to the Son,<br />
Come I to the Holy Spirit powerful;<br />
Come I this day with God,<br />
Come I this day with Christ,<br />
Come I with the Spirit of kindly balm,</p>
<p>God, and Spirit, and Jesus,<br />
From the crown of my head<br />
To the soles of my feet;<br />
Come I with my reputation,<br />
Come I with my testimony,<br />
Come I to Thee, Jesu--<br />
     Jesu, shelter me.</p></td>
</tr>
